[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man in hospital after Chesterfield crutch attack

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man who was attacked with a crutch is in hospital in a serious condition.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 39-year-old victim was hit over the head on Monday afternoon in Chesterfield, Derbyshire.
A 27-year-old man was arrested on suspicion of assault and is being questioned by police.
Derbyshire Constabulary appealed for witnesses to the assault, which happened at 15:30 BST in Beetwell Street, to contact them.
